# ── Free LLM Provider Keys ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Add at least one. All are free-tier with daily/per-minute limits.
# Fastest for Pi Zero 2W (lowest first-token latency):

GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...          # https://console.groq.com/keys  — daily reset
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...        # https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...          # any GitHub PAT — free with any account

# ── Optional providers ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...  # https://openrouter.ai/keys
# CEREBRAS_API_KEY=csk-...      # https://cloud.cerebras.ai
# MISTRAL_API_KEY=...           # https://console.mistral.ai
# NVIDIA_API_KEY=nvapi-...      # https://build.nvidia.com
# COHERE_API_KEY=...            # https://dashboard.cohere.com
# HF_API_KEY=hf_...             # https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens

# ── Multiple keys (key rotation) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# The proxy supports numbered key variants and rotates across them on 429.
# Add _2, _3, … variants and the proxy discovers them automatically.
#
# GROQ_API_KEY_2=gsk_...
# GROQ_API_KEY_3=gsk_...
# GEMINI_API_KEY_2=AIza...
# GITHUB_TOKEN_2=ghp_...
#
# LEGITIMATE USE: different keys from different people on the same setup
# (household members, teammates) where each person signed up independently.
#
# WARNING: Creating multiple accounts with the same provider solely to
# bypass rate limits or multiply free-tier quota most likely violates that
# provider's Terms of Service. Doing so is entirely at your own risk and
# may result in all associated accounts being permanently banned.
# This project takes no responsibility for ToS violations or account loss.
